are being given, “access to government-supported,

206
00:06:27,290 --> 00:06:30,590
low-cost wind and solar electricity.”

207
00:06:30,590 --> 00:06:31,900
Powering the computer servers

208
00:06:31,900 --> 00:06:34,270
is one of the biggest financial challenges

209
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:36,320
to Bitcoin mining.

210
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:37,490
The People’s Bank of China

211
00:06:37,490 --> 00:06:39,800
could also be showing favor to Bitcoin.

212
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:40,990
A senior banking official

213
00:06:40,990 --> 00:06:43,650
