214
00:06:43,650 --> 00:06:45,460
about all the advantages Bitcoin

215
00:06:45,460 --> 00:06:47,460
can offer China.

216
00:06:47,460 --> 00:06:48,460
Because if you look at it,

217
00:06:48,460 --> 00:06:50,330
since China can have a huge impact

218
00:06:50,330 --> 00:06:51,729
on the price of Bitcoin,

219
00:06:51,729 --> 00:06:53,580
why wouldn’t the Chinese regime

220
00:06:53,580 --> 00:06:55,680
use its influence over the market

221
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,000
