222
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:59,659
Here’s what the CCP could do.

223
00:06:59,659 --> 00:07:02,250
Let’s say the Bank of China makes it known

224
00:07:02,250 --> 00:07:03,880
they’ll be investigating

225
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:06,770
some major Bitcoin exchange.

226
00:07:06,770 --> 00:07:08,620
Prices plummet.

227
00:07:08,620 --> 00:07:10,770
Chinese officials then buy up Bitcoin

228
00:07:10,770 --> 00:07:12,480
while the market is down.

229
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,510
And then they release a statement

230
00:07:13,510 --> 00:07:16,170
that the Chinese government supports Bitcoin,

231
00:07:16,170 --> 00:07:19,600
and the market skyrockets.

232
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,600
Again, that’s hypothetical,

233
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,199
but very possible.

234
00:07:22,199 --> 00:07:24,210
Following China’s investigation earlier

235
00:07:24,210 --> 00:07:25,210
