237
00:07:26,770 --> 00:07:29,800
to about $2,900 over the last three months.”

238
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,900
And on top of that,

239
00:07:31,900 --> 00:07:32,900
the Chinese regime has

240
00:07:32,900 --> 00:07:34,800
the ultimate Sword of Damocles

241
