Which will, of course, further drive up the
price.

251
00:07:57,820 --> 00:08:01,090
Possibly making some officials very rich.

252
00:08:01,090 --> 00:08:04,020
Of course, China is not the only influence

253
00:08:04,020 --> 00:08:05,490
on the Bitcoin market,

254
00:08:05,490 --> 00:08:07,990
